INSERT INTO `page` VALUES (704, NULL, NULL, NULL, 17, 8, 192, '查看個人信息', '##### 簡要描述\n\n- 獲取個人信息接口，用於獲取用戶基本信息（如：用戶套餐等）\n\n##### 請求URI\n- ` /api/v1/account/view `\n  \n##### 請求方式\n- GET\n\n#### 請求頭\n\n- greycdn-token: 1d2n3j9x-wjeg-469a-9a3b-033sd909qd91\n\n> *greycdn-token: 這是使用用戶的API Token, API Token 格式為c6fb127e-3848-4sh2-98d9-cbe1238jdj44e5\n\n- User-Agent Greypanel-CDN-API-V2\n\n> *請求時，需要添加UA請求頭以通過請求的有效性識別，此請求需應用於所有API調用請求，否者請求則會被攔截\n\n\n#### 請求示例\n```\ncurl -X GET https://api2.greypanel.com/api/v1/account/view\n-H \"greycdn-token: 1d2n3j9x-wjeg-469a-9a3b-033sd909qd91\"\n-H \"User-Agent: Greypanel-CDN-API-V2\"     \n```\n\n##### 返回示例 \n\n``` \n{\n  \"result\": {\n    \"userName\": \"sample-test\",\n    \"userType\": \"正式用户\",\n    \"email\": \"sample@greypanel.com\",\n    \"mobile\": \"\",\n    \"packageInfo\": {\n      \"apiBalance\": {\n        \"totalAmount\": \"10\",\n        \"usedAmount\": \"10\"\n      },\n      \"portBalance\": {\n        \"totalAmount\": \"100\",\n        \"usedAmount\": \"3\"\n      },\n      \"portProxyBalance\": {\n        \"totalAmount\": \"101\",\n        \"usedAmount\": \"0\"\n      },\n      \"bandWidthBalance\": {\n        \"totalAmount\": \"0\",\n        \"usedAmount\": \"0.0\"\n      },\n      \"certBalance\": {\n        \"totalAmount\": \"100\",\n        \"usedAmount\": \"12\"\n      },\n      \"domainBalance\": {\n        \"totalAmount\": \"600\",\n        \"usedAmount\": \"3\"\n      },\n      \"defenceBalance\": {\n        \"totalAmount\": \"0\",\n        \"usedAmount\": \"-\"\n      },\n      \"subAccountBalance\": {\n        \"totalAmount\": \"20\",\n        \"usedAmount\": \"9\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"limitMcnCerts\": 0,\n    \"mainlandOpt\": 0,\n    \"mcnFlag\": 0,\n    \"probationFlag\": 0,\n    \"probationStartDate\": null,\n    \"probationEndDate\": null,\n    \"probationPeriod\": null,\n    \"officialStartDate\": \"2018/08/01\",\n    \"timeZone\": \"-8\",\n    \"lang\": \"zh\",\n    \"description\": null\n  },\n  \"response\": \"success\",\n  \"message\": \"\"\n}\n```\n\n\n##### 返回參數說明\n\n|參數名稱|描述|\n|:----- |:-----|----- |\n| userType |使用者類型 |\n| packageInfo |套餐信息 |\n| apiBalance |API額度 |\n| portBalance | 端口額度 |\n| bandWidthBalance | 帶寬額度 |\n|certBalance | 證書額度度 |\n|domainBalance | 域名額度 |\n|defenceBalance | 防禦額度 |\n|totalAmount| 總額度|\n|usedAmount| 已使用|\n|mainlandOpt| 大陸線路優化|\n|probationStartDate |測試開始時間|\n|probationEndDate| 測試結束時間|\n|probationPeriod |測試週期|\n|officialStartDate| 正式啟用時間|\n|timeZone| 時區|\n|lang |語言|\n\n\n', 99, 0, NULL, NULL, 3, 0);
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES (705, NULL, NULL, NULL, 17, 8, 193, 'Introduction', '&lt;div  style=&quot;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\n![](/upload/608b65c997fea.png)\n&lt;/div&gt;\n\nGreypanel CDN service system is an intelligent network service system independently developed by Greypanel with independent intellectual property rights. The original intention of its design is to improve the customer\'s website access speed while improving the defense performance of the customer\'s website, so as to achieve faster and safer information transmission between the server and the client.\n\nThe Greypanel CDN service system monitors the distribution of customer traffic in real time, the load status of each node, and each node calculates complex data such as the end user\'s corresponding time, and then automatically schedules its nodes covering the entire network, which is based on the existing Internet. Construct a layer of intelligent virtual network to direct the end user\'s request to the node closest to it and the fastest responding node. Help customers avoid Internet congestion and provide users with a fast access experience.\n\nAt the same time, the Greypanel CDN service system has a global node network and cleaning center as well as a complete WAF firewall to provide security guarantees for customer websites. Through intelligent shunt cleaning, it realizes active defense against DDoS attacks while hiding the source of customers, allowing customers to be attacked while ensuring that the website can still be accessed quickly and effectively.\n\nThis document introduces and demonstrates the client server side of Greypanel CDN service system. Users can configure their system according to relevant demonstrations. This operation guide document will cover 90% of user service functions, realize configuration self-service and service customization, so as to significantly improve user experience. Functions include login, home page, service configuration, statistical analysis, user center management, etc.\n\nGreypanel System Address：https://console.greypanel.com', 99, 0, NULL, NULL, 2, 0);
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES (706, NULL, NULL, NULL, 17, 8, 193, 'Request API Token', '\n\n    \n##### Description\n\n- This Interface Is used to request API token\n\n##### Request URI\n- ` /api/v1/token/request `\n  \n##### Request Method\n- POST\n\n##### Parameter Description\n\n|Parameter|Required|Type|Description|\n|:---- |:---|:----- |----- |\n|type |Yes |string | normal（管理員），viewer (客戶) |\n\n#### Request Example\n``` \ncurl -X POST http://api2.greypanel.com/api/v1/token/request\n-H \"greycdn-token: 1d2n3j9x-wjeg-469a-9a3b-033sd909qd91\"\n-H \"User-Agent: Greypanel-CDN-API-V2\"\n-d \'{\"type\":\"normal\"}\'\n``` \n\n##### Response Example\n\n``` \n{\n  \"result\": {\n    \"id\": \"966bbf22-aff8-4138-9f25-3fa2f139764c\",\n    \"token\": \"08c1a939-4ac1-43b7-b6e0-a740024361e3\",\n    \"userType\": \"normal\",\n    \"userId\": 781,\n    \"expiryDate\": \"2120/05/17 10:05:05\",\n    \"createDate\": \"2021/05/17 10:05:05\",\n    \"modifyDate\": null\n  },\n  \"response\": \"success\",\n  \"message\": \"申请成功\"\n}\n```\n\n\n\n', 99, 0, NULL, NULL, 2, 0);
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES (707, NULL, NULL, NULL, 17, 8, 194, 'Record List', '\n##### Description\n\n- This Interface Is Used To View The Record List Function In DNS Record Management\n\n#####  Request URI\n- ` /api/v1/domain/list`\n  \n##### Request Method\n- POST \n\n#### Request Head\n\n- greycdn-token: 1d2n3j9x-wjeg-469a-9a3b-033sd909qd91\n\n> *greycdn-token: This Is Using User Based API Token, API Token format as c6fb127e-3848-4sh2-98d9-cbe1238jdj44e5\n\n- User-Agent Greypanel-CDN-API-V2\n\n> *When Makaking Request，Its a Must To Provide UA Head For Identification and Its Also Required For Others API Requests, Otherwise Request Will Be Intercept.\n\n##### Parameter Description\n\n|Parameter|Required|Type|Description|\n|:----    |:---|:----- |-----   |\n|desc  |Yes  |string |desc    |\n|page  |Yes  |string |page    |\n|pageSize  |Yes  |string |pageSize    |\n|sort  |Yes  |string |sort    |\n\n#### Request Example \n``` \ncurl -X POST --header \'greycdn-token: 1d2n3j9x-wjeg-469a-9a3b-033sd909qd91\' --header \'User-Agent: Greypanel-CDN-API-V2\'  -d \'{\n  \"keyWord\": \"\",     \n  \"searchPage\": {                          \n    \"desc\": 1,\n    \"page\": 1,\n    \"pageSize\": 10,\n    \"sort\": \"\"\n  }\n}\' \'http://api2.greypanel.com/api/v1/domain/list\'\n``` \n\n##### Response Example \n\n``` \n{\n  \"result\" : {\n    \"number\" : 0,\n    \"size\" : 10,\n    \"totalPages\" : 1,\n    \"numberOfElements\" : 1,\n    \"totalElements\" : 1,\n    \"sort\" : null,\n    \"content\" : [ {\n      \"uid\" : \"uid\",\n      \"name\" : \"www.baidu.com\",\n      \"displayName\" : \"www.baidu.com\",\n      \"masterName\" : \"baidu.com\",\n      \"masterDisplayName\" : \"baidu.com\",\n      \"sslEnable\" : -1,\n      \"siteUid\" : \"siteUid\",\n      \"siteName\" : \"test-sample\",\n      \"siteUniqueName\" : \"siteUniqueName\",\n      \"status\" : 0,\n      \"forceHttps\" : 1,\n      \"moveFlag\" : 1,\n      \"dnsStatus\" : 0,\n      \"dnsResult\" : \"\",\n      \"sourceI