INSERT INTO `page` VALUES (708, NULL, NULL, NULL, 17, 8, 194, 'Add Record', '\n##### Description\n\n- This Interface Is Used To Add DNS Management Records\n\n#####  Request URI\n- ` /api/v1/domain/create `\n  \n##### Request Method\n- POST \n\n#### Request Head\n\n- greycdn-token: 1d2n3j9x-wjeg-469a-9a3b-033sd909qd91\n\n> *greycdn-token: This Is Using User Based API Token, API Token format as c6fb127e-3848-4sh2-98d9-cbe1238jdj44e5\n\n- User-Agent Greypanel-CDN-API-V2\n\n> *When Makaking Request，Its a Must To Provide UA Head For Identification and Its Also Required For Others API Requests, Otherwise Request Will Be Intercept.\n\n\n##### Parameter Description\n\n|Parameter|Required|Type|Description|\n|:----    |:---|:----- |-----   |\n|displayName |Yes  |string |displayName   |\n|sslEnable  |Yes  |integer | sslEnable    |\n|uid |Yes  |string |uid   |\n\n#### Request Example \n``` \ncurl -X POST  --header \'greycdn-token: 1d2n3j9x-wjeg-469a-9a3b-033sd909qd91\' --header \'User-Agent: Greypanel-CDN-API-V2\'  -d \'{\n  \"displayName\": \"www.sample.com\",\n  \"sslEnable\": 0\n}\' \'http://api2.greypanel.com/api/v1/domain/create?uid=339e59f4-cb38-4550-8303-8ff37e3fbc92\'\n``` \n\n##### Response Example \n\n``` \n{\n  \"result\" : [ {\n    \"uid\" : \"uid\",\n    \"name\" : \"www.sample.com\",\n    \"displayName\" : \"www.sample.com\",\n    \"masterName\" : \"sample.com\",\n    \"masterDisplayName\" : \"sample.com\",\n    \"sslEnable\" : 0,\n    \"siteUid\" : \"siteUid\",\n    \"siteName\" : \"test-sample\",\n    \"siteUniqueName\" : \"siteUniqueName\",\n    \"status\" : 0,\n    \"forceHttps\" : 0,\n    \"moveFlag\" : 0,\n    \"dnsStatus\" : 0,\n    \"sourceIp\" : \"sample.com:80\",\n    \"protocol\" : \"http\",\n    \"sslAuto\" : 0,\n    \"createDate\" : \"2021/05/05 09:20:20\"\n  } ],\n  \"response\" : \"success\",\n  \"message\" : \"\"\n}\n```\n#### Response Data Description\n|  Key | Description  |\n| :------------ | :------------ |\n|uid|	站点uid|\n|name|	主机记录值|\n|displa